text: Aaliyah Powell (born 25 October 2002) is a British taekwondo practitioner. She won a bronze medal in bantamweight at the 2019 World Taekwondo Championships, after being defeated by Tatiana Kudashova in the semifinal. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:British female taekwondo practitioners Category:Taekwondo practitioners at the 2018 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
